":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":20082074,"talkid":78445,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/401306.html?thread=20082074#t20082074","above":20081562,"upictitle":"George R.R. Martin: Spain","article":"You can buy signed books -- by me, and a host of other fine authors -- from the Jean Cocteau Cinema.<br /><br />Many of the available titles are listed on the Cocteau website, but others have not been put up yet.  But if you email them and inquire, you may be able to find what you want.<br /><br />(The books are autographed, but not personalized or inscribed.  I can no longer offer that service, sorry.  I have no plans to reopen my own online book sale page).<br /><br />Houston?  No.  But I will be in Nacogdoches in late February, that's close.  Check my website for details.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"2 years ago","ctime":"January 11 2015, 06:10:12 UTC","parent":20081562,"massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"grrm","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"grrm","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"grrm","ctime_ts":1420956612,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/124388450/73667894","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/401306.html?thread=20082842#t20082842","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/401306.html?thread=20082842#t20082842","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/401306.html?thread=20082842#t20082842","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"nelson_rathbone","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://nelson-rathbo